Hello! I'm hitting a problem where my theme is trying to load in a Google font when I'm using an Adobe font, so it's giving me a 404 error in the console.

The Adobe font is loading and working fine, but I can't get rid of the Google font links in the header. I have my typography setup like this in fields.json:

```{
        "label": "Primary",
        "name": "primary",
        "load_external_fonts" : false,
        "type": "font",
        "visibility": {
          "hidden_subfields": {
            "bold": true,
            "italic": true,
            "size": true,
            "underline": true,
            "font": true
          }
        },
        "default": {
          "color": "#231f20",
          "fallback": "sans-serif",
          "font": "Avenir Book",
          "font_set": "ADOBE",
          "variant": "400"
        }```
